config.prompt:
Analyze the following lead information and provide a qualification assessment:

Company: {{input.company_name}}
Industry: {{input.industry}}
Company Size: {{input.company_size}}
Job Title: {{input.job_title}}
Lead Source: {{input.lead_source}}
Notes: {{input.notes}}

Provide:
1. Lead Score (1-100)
2. Qualification Status (Hot/Warm/Cold)
3. Key Strengths (what makes this lead promising)
4. Potential Concerns (risks or gaps)
5. Recommended Next Steps (specific actions)
6. Ideal Product Fit (if applicable)
